{"type":"text","timestamp":1775888786260,"sessionID":"ses_284cb428affeGVUfHAJ7DosiOQ","part":{"id":"prt_d7b37fce1001H6tjB9q05qi71q","messageID":"msg_d7b37b7ff0018OLdW0jeXd37xa","sessionID":"ses_284cb428affeGVUfHAJ7DosiOQ","type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me compile the verification report.\n\n---\n\n## AR-038 Spec Verification Report\n\n### 1. Clientset (`client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n\n| Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Interface` with `Discovery()` + `RuntimeV1alpha1()` | ✅ PASS | Matches spec exactly (`clientset.go:30-33`) |\n| `Clientset` struct with embedded `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` + `runtimeV1alpha1` | ✅ PASS | Matches spec (`clientset.go:36-39`) |\n| `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)` | ✅ PASS | `clientset.go:55` |\n| `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client)` | ✅ PASS | `clientset.go:78` |\n| `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset` | ✅ PASS | `clientset.go:101` |\n| `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset` | ✅ PASS | `clientset.go:110` |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1()` accessor | ✅ PASS | `clientset.go:42` |\n\n### 2. Typed Client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\n\n| Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` interface | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Missing `RESTClient() rest.Interface` method (`interfaces.go:34-37`) |\n| `AgentRuntimeInterface` — Create/Update/UpdateStatus/Delete/Get/List/Watch/Patch | ✅ PASS | All 8 methods present (`interfaces.go:12-21`) |\n| `AgentRuntimeInterface` — `DeleteCollection` | ❌ FAIL | **Missing from interface and implementation** |\n| `AgentRuntimeInterface` — `AgentRuntimeExpansion` embedding | ❌ FAIL | **Missing from interface** |\n| `CodeInterpreterInterface` — same CRUD methods | ✅ PASS | All 8 methods present (`interfaces.go:23-32`) |\n| `CodeInterpreterInterface` — `DeleteCollection` | ❌ FAIL | **Missing from interface and implementation** |\n| REST resource plural `agentruntimes` | ✅ PASS | `client.go:11` |\n| REST resourc